step 1 - open vscode terminal
' npm init -y ' 

step 2 - installing tailwind css 

npm install -D tailwindcss

npx tailwindcss init  
step 3 - create input.css file and add utilities file of tailwind 

@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

step 4 - open package.json 

add below content in script section replacing with test

"build": "tailwindcss -i ./input.css -o ./css/main.css",
    "watch": "tailwindcss -i ./input.css -o ./css/main.css --watch"

 step 4 - once done run " npm run build  "

   step 5 - create index.html add some code and run "npm run watch"   

# to add custom colors  go to tailwind.config.js 
 add in extend section